The use of evacuation times and capacity constraints suggests cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) as a possible sub-category. The paper also involves optimization of sink locations, which suggests cs.RO (Robotics) as a possible sub-category. Finally, the paper involves uncertainty in vertex supplies, which suggests cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) as a possible sub-category.
